  "subject": "Shorten key length for crypto junit to 128 bits",
  "commit_message": "Shorten key length for crypto junit to 128 bits\n\nDue to import restrictions, java may not be configured to allow 256-bit\nkeys.  The key used in the junit was shortened to 128 bits so that it\nwould work whether or not 256-bit keys are enabled.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-1945\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\nChange-Id: I160eaacd09b383b4b80e684ddf98e02ffc938d11\n",
